#### 1.3 App.css Cleanup

**File: `/app/src/App.css`** -- The current file constrains `#root` with `max-width: 1280px`, `padding: 2rem`, and `text-align: center`. This should be cleared entirely (the file should be empty or removed), since layout will be handled per-page.

